flowchart TD

A[Scene load: Pacman] --> AW[GameManager.Awake<br/>singleton + FilterEnabledGhosts<br/>build Score/Lives/UI managers]
AW --> ST[GameManager.Start<br/>score=0, lives=3]
ST --> NR[NewRound]
NR --> NRACT[Hide GameOver,<br/>reactivate all pellets,<br/>ResetState ghosts & Pac-Man]
NRACT --> SPEED[ApplyRoundSpeeds<br/>per-round curve from GameSettings]
SPEED --> LOOP[Unity game loop<br/>Update / FixedUpdate]

LOOP --> PAUSE{Esc pressed?}
PAUSE -- Yes --> PAUSED[PauseManager.Pause<br/>Time.timeScale = 0]
PAUSED --> PMENU{User choice}
PMENU -- Resume --> LOOP
PMENU -- Quit --> ACCUEIL[Load PageAccueil scene]

PAUSE -- No --> MOVE[Pac-Man: HandleInput WASD/arrows<br/>or PacmanAgent if aiControlled]
MOVE --> GMOVE[Ghosts pick direction at Nodes<br/>via active GhostBehavior]
GMOVE --> PHYS[Movement.FixedUpdate<br/>Rigidbody2D.MovePosition]
PHYS --> COL{Unity collision / trigger}

COL -- Pellet trigger --> PEAT[GameManager.PelletEaten<br/>deactivate + Add points]
PEAT --> REM{Pellets remaining?}
REM -- Yes --> LOOP
REM -- No --> RC[currentRound++, OnRoundComplete<br/>Invoke NewRound after 3s]
RC --> NR

COL -- PowerPellet trigger --> PPEAT[GameManager.PowerPelletEaten]
PPEAT --> FRIGHT[Enable Frightened on all ghosts<br/>for pellet.duration, multiplier reset timer]
FRIGHT --> PEAT

COL -- Ghost collision --> GSTATE{Ghost frightened?}
GSTATE -- Yes --> GE[GameManager.GhostEaten<br/>Add points * ghostMultiplier++]
GE --> GHOME[Ghost teleports to home, returns]
GHOME --> LOOP
GSTATE -- No --> PE[GameManager.PacmanEaten<br/>lives--]
PE --> LIVES{Lives > 0?}
LIVES -- Yes --> DEATH[Pac-Man DeathSequence<br/>Invoke ResetState after 3s]
DEATH --> LOOP
LIVES -- No --> OVER[GameOver<br/>show panel, Time.timeScale = 0]

COL -- Passage trigger --> WARP[Passage teleports to connection]
WARP --> LOOP
COL -- None --> LOOP
